    <div class="govuk-grid-row">
      <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
        <p class="govuk-body">
          Empathy builds trust and respect among people. The more empathy someone has the better they will want to treat others. By using these activities in the classroom you can improve the behaviour of your pupils. 
        </p>
